HEADWORD: Torchwood
<hw>Torch"wood`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>The inflammable wood of certain trees (<spn>Amyris
balsamifera</spn>, <spn>Amyris Floridana</spn>, etc.); also, the trees
themselves.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

